The <b>Royal Commission on Civil Liability and Compensation for Personal Injury</b>, better known as the <b>Pearson commission</b> was a <autocracy wordnetid="108361001" confidence="0.8">
<system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
